meta.description:
A new study published in the New England Journal of Medicine (NEJM) shows not only that the effectiveness of the Pfizer Covid vaccine becomes negative (meaning the vaccinated are more likely to be infected than the unvaccinated) within five months but that the vaccine destroys any protection a person has from natural immunity.

Read more here: 
https://www.infowars.com/posts/covid-vaccine-destroys-natural-immunity-nejm-study-shows/

https://www.infowars.com/posts/desantis-medical-elites-were-wrong-about-efficacy-of-mrna-vaccines/

https://www.infowars.com/posts/watch-romanian-mep-blasts-moderna-and-astrazeneca-in-eu-parliament-over-covid-vaccine/

https://www.infowars.com/posts/covid-vaccines-up-to-100-times-more-likely-to-cause-serious-injury-to-a-young-adult-than-prevent-it-say-top-scientists/

title: Covid Vaccine Destroys Natural Immunity, NEJM Study Shows
